ns0:foreignObject.html:div: Look carefully at the image showing the elements of the weather. Use what you see to answer the questions. You can use your knowledge from science class to help you.

ns0:svg.ns0:text: 1. What are the main things you see in the picture related to the weather?
2. Can you point out and name the different elements shown in the image that make up the weather?
3. What do you think the weather is like in the picture? Is it sunny, rainy, or something else?
4. How do the elements of the weather in the picture affect the people or objects shown?
5. If you were to draw a continuation of this picture, what other weather elements might you include and why?
